{
  "stem": "2533.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's like a big bed in front of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were flowers, always were planted flowers-- I don't know who was doing that-- and a very big memorial.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we brought over with us candles and flowers and all that we put there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Jules had a video recorder, so he had it all-- all on the video.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've got it too on the video.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He made me a copy of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But 18 months ago, I went with my family for the 50th anniversary of the escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The commemoration was beautifully, beautifully done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "First the entrance with the flags there, Israeli flags and the Polish flags.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Polish military had it all arranged with a band, and they had from America a hazzan and a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was other American.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The one people who-- they are on the international committee who preserves war places, where they wouldn't be demolished and all that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was a lot-- a lot of other-- from other countries people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And wreath laying was almost all from Warsaw, the ambassadors, not the ambassadors themselves, but they were sending there with wreaths were laid there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then there was the gun salute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the orchestra was playing all the time, the drums, whenever somebody was going there with the flowers to lay on the graves, because there isn't-- there aren't any graves.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But where the camp was, the Germans demolished everything, and they planted trees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it's a forest now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There's not much clearing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the rail is still there and the station is still there.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
